 Kinetic Sports Management, the organisers of the annual Copa Lagos beach soccer event have commended its sponsors for their financial and material support that made this year’s edition of the championship the best. Copa Lagos 2019 saw FCMB, Pepsi and BetKing and Eko Atlantic doing a lot to enhance the experience of fans with lots of fun and excitement. Top artistes, games, food and lots of other events were on parade to keep their guests and fans excited throughout the tournament. Over the last 8 years, Copa Lagos has grown from strength to strength leading to the general view where it has been adjudged as a World Class event and placed on the map of global tourism through the merger of beach culture and lifestyle. The Management of Kinetic Sports is determined to ensure that Copa Lagos meets the social and economic values for all stakeholders. An avenue for brands to engage and connect with their targeted market to understand the behavior and consumption preferences and finally where the “SMEs have the window to also showcase their products and services.” The organizers are also using this medium to call on other multinationals to support the initiative that promotes youth, sports and national development in order to enhance the Nigeria sports and tourism sectors.